column7:
Mapeo DB:
SELECT b.BRANCH_NAME, COUNT(o.ORDER_ID) FROM ORDERS o 
JOIN BRANCHES b ON o.BRANCH_ID = b.BRANCH_ID GROUP BY b.BRANCH_NAME;
